{
  "info": {
    "name": "Ziovpo Backend API",
    "description": "Как пользоваться\n========\n\n**Сценарий (Е2Е)** — одна папка «Сценарий (Е2Е, весь поток)»: все шаги лабы по порядку (регистрация первого админа → лицензии). Удобно запускать через **Collection Runner** только на этой папке.\n• Заполните в переменных коллекции **authPassword** (и при желании authUsername, authEmail).\n• Если в БД **уже есть** пользователи: в Runner **снимите галочку** с «01 Регистрация…» и **включите** «02 Login…» (или сначала один раз выполните Login вручную из папки «Аутентификация»).\n\n**Остальное** — папки ниже: любой запрос по отдельности (логин, refresh, второй пользователь, каталог, лицензии, устройства, проверка 403).\n\nПеременные: baseUrl, authUsername, authPassword, authEmail; для второго пользователя — userUsername, userPassword, userEmail. Токены пишутся в переменные коллекции из тестов. Первый зарегистрированный = ROLE_ADMIN.\n\nHTTPS: при самоподписанном сертификате отключите Postman → Settings → SSL certificate verification.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {"key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "authUsername", "value": "admin", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "authPassword", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "authEmail", "value": "admin@lab.local", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "userUsername", "value": "ivan", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "userPassword", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "userEmail", "value": "ivan@lab.local", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "accessToken", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "holderAccessToken", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "adminAccessToken", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "refreshToken", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "holderUserId", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "productId", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "licenseTypeId", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "licenseCode", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "licenseId", "value": "", "type": "string"},
    {"key": "deviceId", "value": "", "type": "string"}
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{"key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string"}]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Сценарий (Е2Е, весь поток)",
      "description": "Полный поток задания: регистрация (первый = ADMIN) **или** login → me → каталог → создание лицензии → устройство → activate → verify → renew.\n\n**Collection Runner:** выберите только эту папку. Пустая БД: оставьте 01, **отключите 02 Login**. Уже есть пользователи: **отключите 01**, **включите 02 Login**.",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{"key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string"}]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "01 Регистрация (первый = ADMIN)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('adminAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{authUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{authPassword}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{authEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "02 Login (если БД уже не пустая — вместо 01)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('adminAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{authUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{authPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "03 GET /api/me → holderUserId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderUserId', pm.response.json().id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/me"}
        },
        {
          "name": "04 POST /api/admin/catalog/products",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('productId', pm.response.json().id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Demo Antivirus\"\n}"},
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/catalog/products"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "05 POST /api/admin/catalog/license-types",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('licenseTypeId', pm.response.json().id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Standard\",\n  \"defaultDurationInDays\": 365,\n  \"description\": \"1 year default\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/catalog/license-types"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "06 POST /api/licenses (создать)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('licenseCode', j.code);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('licenseId', j.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{holderUserId}}\",\n  \"ownerId\": \"{{holderUserId}}\",\n  \"productId\": \"{{productId}}\",\n  \"typeId\": \"{{licenseTypeId}}\",\n  \"deviceCount\": 3,\n  \"description\": \"Lab demo license\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "07 POST /api/devices",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('deviceId', pm.response.json().id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"PC-Lab\",\n  \"macAddress\": \"00:11:22:33:44:55\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/devices"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "08 POST /api/licenses/activate",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(j.ticket).to.exist;",
                  "    pm.expect(j.signatureBase64).to.be.a('string');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"{{licenseCode}}\",\n  \"deviceId\": \"{{deviceId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/activate"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "09 POST /api/licenses/verify",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"{{licenseCode}}\",\n  \"deviceId\": \"{{deviceId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/verify"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "10 POST /api/licenses/renew",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"{{licenseCode}}\",\n  \"extendDays\": 30\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/renew"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Аутентификация (по отдельности)",
      "description": "Отдельные вызовы без прохождения всего сценария.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/register (первый = ADMIN)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('adminAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{authUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{authPassword}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{authEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/register (USER)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{userUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{userPassword}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/login (authUsername)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('adminAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{authUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{authPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/login (userUsername)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{userUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{userPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/refresh",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('adminAccessToken', json.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"},
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Демо и роли (по отдельности)",
      "description": "Нужен accessToken (после login/register).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/me",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('holderUserId', pm.response.json().id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/me"}
        },
        {"name": "GET /api/profile", "request": {"method": "GET", "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/profile"}},
        {
          "name": "GET /api/admin/ping (ожидается 200 для ADMIN)",
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/ping"}
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/admin/ping (ожидается 403 для USER)",
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/ping"}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Каталог admin (по отдельности)",
      "description": "ROLE_ADMIN. Токен первого пользователя или после login authUsername.",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{"key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string"}]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Создать продукт",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Demo Antivirus\"\n}"},
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/catalog/products"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Создать тип лицензии",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Standard\",\n  \"defaultDurationInDays\": 365,\n  \"description\": \"1 year\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/catalog/license-types"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Лицензии (по отдельности)",
      "description": "Подставьте UUID вручную или используйте переменные после сценария / GET me.",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{"key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string"}]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Создать лицензию",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{holderUserId}}\",\n  \"ownerId\": \"{{holderUserId}}\",\n  \"productId\": \"{{productId}}\",\n  \"typeId\": \"{{licenseTypeId}}\",\n  \"deviceCount\": 3,\n  \"description\": \"manual\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Активировать",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"{{licenseCode}}\",\n  \"deviceId\": \"{{deviceId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/activate"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Проверить",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"{{licenseCode}}\",\n  \"deviceId\": \"{{deviceId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/verify"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Продлить",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"{{licenseCode}}\",\n  \"extendDays\": 30\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/licenses/renew"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Устройства (по отдельности)",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{"key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string"}]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Зарегистрировать устройство",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"PC-1\",\n  \"macAddress\": \"AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/devices"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
